{
  "meta": {
    "is_partial": true,
    "description": "댓글 섹션 전체"
  },
  "type": "basic",
  "name": "Div",
  "props": {
    "className": "card bg-base-100 shadow-sm"
  },
  "children": [
    {
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "H3",
      "props": {
        "className": "text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white flex items-center justify-between px-6 pt-6 pb-4"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "props": { "className": "flex items-center gap-2" },
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "composite",
              "name": "Icon",
              "props": {
                "name": "message-square",
                "size": "lg"
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "text": "$t:board.comments"
            },
            {
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Span",
              "text": "{{(post?.data?.comments ?? []).length}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "comment": "삭제된 댓글 포함 토글 버튼 (manager 권한 보유 시에만 표시)",
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Button",
          "if": "{{post?.data?.abilities?.can_manage}}",
          "props": {
            "type": "button",
            "className": "{{query.del_cmt === '1' ? 'inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 border-2 border-blue-600 dark:border-blue-400 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30 text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-300 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium' : 'inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-2 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 rounded-lg text-sm hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700'}}"
          },
          "actions": [
            {
              "type": "click",
              "handler": "navigate",
              "params": {
                "path": "/board/{{route.slug}}/{{route.id}}",
                "mergeQuery": true,
                "query": {
                  "del_cmt": "{{query.del_cmt === '1' ? '' : '1'}}"
                }
              }
            }
          ],
          "children": [
            { "type": "basic", "name": "Icon", "props": { "name": "eye", "size": "sm" } },
            { "type": "basic", "name": "Span", "text": "$t:board.filter.include_deleted_comments" }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "헤더 구분선",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
      }
    },
    {
      "comment": "댓글 없음 안내 (조회+작성 권한 O, 댓글 0개, 블라인드 아님)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{(post?.data?.comments ?? []).length === 0 && post?.data?.abilities?.can_write_comments && post?.data?.status !== 'blinded'}}",
      "props": {
        "className": "px-6 py-8 text-center"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "composite",
          "name": "Icon",
          "props": {
            "name": "message-square",
            "size": "xl",
            "className": "mx-auto text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-600 mb-3"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "P",
          "props": {
            "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          },
          "text": "$t:board.no_comments_yet"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "props": {
        "className": "space-y-4"
      },
      "iteration": {
        "source": "{{post?.data?.comments ?? []}}",
        "item_var": "comment",
        "index_var": "idx"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "Div",
          "if": "{{(comment?.depth ?? 0) === 0 || (_local.collapsedReplies?.[$computed.commentRootMap?.[comment?.id]] === false)}}",
          "props":{
            "className": "border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-700/50 transition-colors {{(comment?.depth ?? 0) > 0 ? 'bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900/50' : ''}}"
          },
          "children": [
            {
              "partial": "partials/board/show/_comment_item.json"
            },
            {
              "comment": "답글이 있는 경우 토글 버튼",
              "type": "basic",
              "name": "Button",
              "if": "{{(comment?.replies_count ?? 0) > 0 && (comment?.depth ?? 0) === 0}}",
              "props": {
                "className": "ml-16 mb-2 text-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-700 dark:hover:text-blue-300 flex items-center gap-1"
              },
              "actions": [
                {
                  "type": "click",
                  "handler": "setState",
                  "params": {
                    "target": "local",
                    "collapsedReplies": "{{Object.assign({}, _local.collapsedReplies || {}, {[comment?.id]: !(_local.collapsedReplies?.[comment?.id] ?? true)})}}"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "composite",
                  "name": "Icon",
                  "props": {
                    "name": "{{_local.collapsedReplies?.[comment?.id] === false ? 'chevron-up' : 'chevron-down'}}",
                    "size": "sm"
                  }
                },
                {
                  "type": "basic",
                  "name": "Span",
                  "text": "{{_local.collapsedReplies?.[comment?.id] === false ? '$t:board.hide_replies' : '$t:board.show_replies'}} ({{comment?.replies_count}})"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "블라인드 게시글 댓글 작성 불가 안내",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{post?.data?.status === 'blinded' && post?.data?.abilities?.can_read_comments}}",
      "props": {
        "className": "px-6 py-8 text-center border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "composite",
          "name": "Icon",
          "props": {
            "name": "eye-slash",
            "size": "xl",
            "className": "mx-auto text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-600 mb-5"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "P",
          "props": {
            "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          },
          "text": "$t:board.blinded_comment_disabled"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "comment": "작성 권한 없음 안내 (조회 권한 O, 작성 권한 X, 블라인드 아님)",
      "type": "basic",
      "name": "Div",
      "if": "{{post?.data?.abilities?.can_read_comments && !post?.data?.abilities?.can_write_comments && post?.data?.status !== 'blinded'}}",
      "props": {
        "className": "px-6 py-8 text-center border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700"
      },
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "composite",
          "name": "Icon",
          "props": {
            "name": "lock",
            "size": "xl",
            "className": "mx-auto text-gray-300 dark:text-gray-600 mb-3"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "basic",
          "name": "P",
          "props": {
            "className": "text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400"
          },
          "text": "$t:board.no_comment_write_permission"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "partial": "partials/board/show/_comment_input.json"
    }
  ]
}